{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"setUser:emails:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUser:emails:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUser:emails:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets user identifier and emails together in a single operation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"userId"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"emails:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"emails"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"emails","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings to associate with the user.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Convenience method that combines "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setUserId:"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"setEmails:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" into a single","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"server request. This is more efficient than calling both methods separately"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and ensures atomic association of user ID with emails."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this during login or registration flows when you have both user ID"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and email available simultaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Complete registration with user ID and emails:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class RegistrationManager {","","    func completeRegistration(_ registration: RegistrationData) {","        \/\/ Create user on backend","        APIClient.shared.createUser(registration) { result in","            guard case .success(let user) = result else { return }","","            \/\/ Set both user ID and emails in single operation","            var emails = [user.email]","            if let secondaryEmail = registration.secondaryEmail {","                emails.append(secondaryEmail)","            }","","            Pushwoosh.configure.setUser(user.id, emails: emails)","","            \/\/ Set initial user tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"registration_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                \"registration_source\": registration.source.rawValue,","                \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","                \"has_completed_onboarding\": false","            ])","        }","    }","}"]},{"code":["   when you need confirmation."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUser:emails:":{"title":"setUser:emails:","abstract":[{"text":"Sets user identifier and emails together in a single operation.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUser:emails:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic"}}}